# EBR : KPI Analysis Deck (Streamlit)

Generate 1–2 adaptive EBR slides with KPI cards, small charts, and embedded screenshots. Outputs a downloadable `.pptx` using your base template.

## 🔧 Setup

1) Clone or fork this repo.
2) (Optional) Create and activate a virtual env.
3) `pip install -r requirements.txt`
4) `streamlit run app.py`

## ☁️ Streamlit Cloud

1) Push this repo to GitHub.
2) On streamlit.io, create a new app -> select this repo -> main branch -> `app.py`.
3) Deploy (no extra secrets required).
4) Upload your base `.pptx` template in the sidebar when running.

## 🧠 Usage

- Upload CSV/XLSX/JSON to map a quick bar/line chart (select x/y columns).
- Add KPI cards (headline, value, short note).
- Upload screenshots; the app embeds them and can place them below cards.
- Click **Generate PPTX** then **Download**.

## 📝 Notes
- Speaker notes are included by default (one bullet per card + chart note).
- If you upload a PPTX template, the output will adopt your brand style.
- No OCR by default; large screenshots can be embedded as-is. You can still crop offline and upload smaller images.

